<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_3.xsd" xmlns:p="tapestry:parameter">
<head>
	<title>Tapestry 5 Hotel Booking - ${pageTitle}</title>
</head>
<body id="homepage">
	<div class="wrapper bs">
		<ul class="topnav">
			<t:security.authenticated>
				<li><span>Welcome ${user?.fullName}</span></li>
				<li>
					<a href="#" t:type="pageLink" t:page="index">Search</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="#" t:type="pageLink" t:page="settings">Settings</a>
				</li>
				<li class="last">
					<a href="#" t:type="actionlink" t:id="logout" id="logout">Log out</a>
				</li>
				<p:else>
					<li>
						<a href="#" t:type="pageLink" t:page="index">Search</a>
					</li>
					<li class="last">
						<t:pageLink page="signin">Log in</t:pageLink>
					</li>
			</p:else>
			</t:security.authenticated>
		</ul>

		<div id="top">

			<h1><img src="${context:/static/tapestry_s.png}" alt="Tapestry" id="tapestry" /></h1>

			<div id="aside">Welcome to the Apache Tapestry 5 Hotel Booking demonstration app</div>
			
			<div class="clearer"></div>

		</div>
		
		<div id="bar">
			<strong>This is a demo app, showing some basic Apache Tapestry
			functionality in the form of hotel booking simulation.</strong>
		</div>
		
		<div class="col">
			<h3 class="first">How this works</h3>
			<p>
				<t:delegate to="sidebar" />
			</p>
		</div>
		
		<div id="content" class="big-col">
			
			<t:body />
			<div class="clearer"></div>			

		</div>		
		
		<div class="clearer"></div>

		<div id="footer">Created with <a href="http://tapestry.apache.org/">Apache Tapestry 5.4</a> and JPA (with Hibernate 3). 
		Get the source code of Hotel Booking at <a href="http://github.com/bobharner/tapestry5-hotel-booking-5.4/">Github</a></div>

	</div>
</body>
</html>
